episodes.title: The Cult of Personality and Spiritual Abuse
episodes.description:
Hi, my name is Dr. Foluso.  I am a licensed psychologist and owner of Skillset Counseling.  In this video I describe what a cult of personality is and how it relates to spiritual abuse.   To book a free one-one-one consultation, go to my website at https://skillsetcounseling.com

*If you or someone you know is in immediate danger, call 911 or go to your nearest emergency room.  You are not entering into a patient-provider relationship by watching this video or reading any content or comments; the video and comments are only for educational purposes and are not clinical recommendations intended for your specific circumstance (s).**

#spiritualabuse
